quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,"“Allah amayambitsa kulenga (zolengedwa), kenako adzabwerezanso (kulengako pambuyo pa imfa yawo), kenako mudzabwezedwa kwa Iye (kuti mudzaweruzidwe)"
  30,12,"“Ndipo tsiku limene nthawi ya chiweruziro (Qiyâma) idzakwana, oipa adzataya mtima (zakupeza mtendere wa Allah)"
  30,13,"“Ndipo sadzakhala ndi aomboli ochokera m’mafano awo, ndipo mafano awowo adzawakana"
  30,14,"“Ndipo tsiku limene nthawi ya chiweruziro (Qiyâma) idzakwana, tsiku limenelo adzalekana (ena kukalowa ku Munda wamtendere, pomwe ena akalowa ku Moto)"
  30,15,"“Koma amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita zabwino, adzakhala m’minda ya zipatso ndi maluwa akusangalatsidwa"
  30,16,"“Ndipo amene sadakhulupirire ndi kutsutsa Ayah Zathu ndi za kukumana ndi tsiku lachimaliziro, iwo adzaperekedwa ku chilango cha Moto"
  30,17,"“Choncho, lemekezani Allah pamene mukulowa m’nthawi za usiku (popemphera Magrbi ndi Isha); ndi pamene mukulowa m’nthawi ya m’bandakucha (popemphera pemphero la Fajr)"
  30,18,"“Kutamandidwa konse, kumwamba ndi pansi nkwa Allah. Ndipo (mulemekezeni) m’nthawi ya madzulo (popemphera Asr) ndi pomwe mukulowa m’nthawi yamasana (Dhuhr)"
  30,19,"“(Iye) amatulutsa chamoyo kuchokera mchakufa, ndipo amatulutsa chakufa kuchokera m’chamoyo, ndipo amaukitsa nthaka pambuyo pa kufa kwake. Ndipo momwemonso mudzatulutsidwa (m’manda)"